**Hey** **${tempVars("username")}!**


PREFIX : `t!`

 
**Information**
`t!`|userinfo : generate information of a user
`t!`|botinfo : generate this bots info
`t!`|channelinfo : generate channel info
`t!`|serverinfo : generate server info

**Economy** 
`t!`| Work : Work for money
`t!`| Crime : Commit a crime then earn money
`t!`| hack : hack an item for cash
`t!`| Shoot  : shoot someone for cash
`t!`| buydog : buy a dog (10k cash needed)

`t!`| petava : set your pets avatar
`t!`| hunt : hunt for cash (dog needed)
`t!`| pay @user : give someone money :)
`t!`| lootbox : collect a lootbox
`t!`| daily : collect your daily (every 24 hours)
`t!`| bet : bet money
`t!`| bal : see your current balance 
`t!`| slut : do naughty things for extra cash
`t!`| bank : see whats in your bank
`t!`| dep : deposit money
`t!`| with : withdraw money
`t!`| ecolb : see who at the top of the economy
`t!`| interest : collect interest of your current bal
`t!`| shop : opens the shop and its buyable items
`t!`| buy : buy an item from the shop
`t!`| mine : mine and find diamonds
`t!`| dsell : sell your diamonds
`t!`| hack : hack someone 
`t!`| shoot : shoot a user




*bot owners only*
`t!`|setgame : sets bots status [example] playing with you
`t!`|setshow : sets bots watch status [example] watching you
